name: Savage
description: 3 phases,each phase has 3 weeks of intense training followed by a deload week,focus of phase one is: Mobilization,Strength and General Prep, Phase 2: Mobilization & Activation, Strength, Hypertrophy
author: Unknown

days.name: Speed And Lower
days.notes: Make sure that you are performing each movement with maximal intensity.  If the set calls for 10 reps that you are performing that set with a weight that you can do only between 8 - 12 reps with.  If you can do more than 12 reps with that weight then you need to move up.

blocks.name: Mobilization
blocks.instructions: No rest between stretches

blocks.name: Speed
blocks.instructions: always make sure to progress to a technical 1 rep max,This means you are maximally performing the drill but not sacrificing any technique.

blocks.name: Strength
blocks.instructions: 2-3 warm-up sets when performing the main compound movement
